1
00:00:27,620 --> 00:00:32,120
Your very first princess summit.
You must be over the moon, Twilight.

2
00:00:32,540 --> 00:00:36,840
I am excited. But, to be honest,
I'm a little nervous, too.

3
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:38,330
You're 'nervicited'!

4
00:00:38,460 --> 00:00:41,560
It's like you wanna jump up and down
and yell "YAY ME!!"

5
00:00:41,690 --> 00:00:44,759
But you also wanna curl up
in a teeny-tiny ball

6
00:00:44,760 --> 00:00:46,860
and hide at the same time!

7
00:00:49,730 --> 00:00:51,980
We've all been there!

8
00:00:52,110 --> 00:00:54,850
I'm there almost every day.

9
00:00:54,980 --> 00:00:58,640
You've got no reason to fret, Twi.
Everything's gonna be just–

10
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:00,150
TWILIGHT!

11
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:02,010
Oh, sorry, darling,

12
00:01:02,140 --> 00:01:05,000
but I just realized
you're not wearing your crown.

13
00:01:05,250 --> 00:01:07,750
You haven't forgotten it
back in Ponyville, have you?

14
00:01:07,750 --> 00:01:08,830
It's in my bag.

15
00:01:10,170 --> 00:01:12,600
Just feel a little self-conscious
about wearing it.

16
00:01:12,730 --> 00:01:15,710
Haven't really gotten accustomed
to these yet, either.

17
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:21,960
You are a princess now, Twilight.
Embrace it!

18
00:01:22,090 --> 00:01:24,870
I'm telling you,
if I had a crown like that,

19
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:27,970
I would never take it off.
Why, I'd sleep in the thing.

20
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:45,790
Her highness,
Princess Twilight Sparkle!

21
00:01:46,780 --> 00:01:50,380
Twilight! I haven't seen you
since the coronation!

22
00:01:50,510 --> 00:01:52,830
We have so much to discuss.

23
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:57,460
But it can wait until tomorrow.
You all look tired from your journey.

24
00:01:57,590 --> 00:01:59,550
Now, off to bed, all of you.

25
00:02:16,490 --> 00:02:17,860
What's wrong, Twilight?

26
00:02:17,990 --> 00:02:21,730
I don't know, Spike.
I'm just... worried I guess.

27
00:02:21,860 --> 00:02:25,020
Princess Cadance was given
the Crystal Empire to rule over.

28
00:02:25,150 --> 00:02:26,616
What if, now that I'm a princess,

29
00:02:26,746 --> 00:02:29,330
Celestia expects me
to lead a kingdom of my own?

30
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:31,790
That would be awesome!

31
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,510
No, it would not!

32
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:36,580
Just because I have this crown
and these wings, it doesn't mean

33
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:38,760
I'll be a good leader!

34
00:02:38,890 --> 00:02:40,540
Aw, sure you will, Twilight.

35
00:02:40,670 --> 00:02:43,070
Now come on,
you should get some shut-eye.

36
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,630
Big day tomorrow!

37
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,600
Can't... tuck...!

38
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:01,330
Just trying to get comfortable!

39
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:21,710
My Little Pony: Equestria Girls
(Spin Off Movie)

40
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,870
Subbed by GrayJeager

41
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:29,000
